projects.name: Laugh Track
projects.description: Laugh Track was my front-end capstone at the Nashville Software School. It is a ReactJS based application that utizlizes JSON, mreh and marrrr. The project was a 2 week sprint and was a practice in CRUD, agile development, wireframing and prototyping. The goal of the app is to help comedians succeed in terms of networking, workshopping material, hosting events and marketing themselves.
